Like, it's so unnecessary in terms of the thinking.

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:47.060
You could just say, these are different ways of thinking.

00:08:47.200 --> 00:08:47.500
Right.

00:08:47.940 --> 00:08:50.800
And this one affords something that this one doesn't afford.

00:08:50.880 --> 00:08:52.540
So you can still make the distinction.

00:08:52.960 --> 00:08:57.040
And again, if he did that, then I would want to say, well, does the distinction really hold

