of the draw, or, like, I would say, like, the performative force of the common, like, the

00:11:13.960 --> 00:11:15.760
infinitive verb, to common.

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:21.460
Like, that paragraph reads, whether we are in any given case capable of thinking, that

